{"tid":827461,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[請預咗輸錢] 李小加：生物科技公司等內地企業在港上市後現「破發潮」難避免","createTime":"2018-09-19T02:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T04:02:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d65909f2ec1a6ea998ac319f9370938d962f52ac","tid":827461,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:50:05.000Z","msg":"內地《財聯社》報道，港交所(<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=LrSPHEXhpvgAHy07SNCmYr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e4b289b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>)  +3.400 (+1.543%)    沽空 $2.18億; 比率 24.515%   行政總裁李小加於中國醫藥創新與投資大會上表示，內地企業包括未有收入的生物科技公司在本港上市後，「破發潮」出現的機會甚高，即股價跌穿招股價的現象。他指有關情況在任何一個市場亦不能倖免，市場需要做好心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，投資於生物科技領域尤其高風險，港交所介入或可減緩「一地雞毛」的發生時間，但仍不能阻止有關情況出現。他又指，不會為生物科技公司引入新的沽空機制，亦不會特地設優惠政策吸引生物科技公司上市，僅是將市場准入制度提升至市場認可的合適水平。(vi/t)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2018-09-18 16:25。)<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.897664/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.897664%2F2&d=LrSPHEXhpvgAHy07SNCmYr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=40d5da71\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.897664/2</a>[/url]"},{"pid":"2225afa8c26e72758409634d45997be3bf68162d","tid":827461,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:51:27.000Z","msg":"賭場同你講贏多d <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fecdf93de9cd34c90a636015eb0472c13d8da1a5","tid":827461,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:54:07.000Z","msg":"1548<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a31a6665ee86734db4fdf392066524fa3e27ea","tid":827461,"uid":85223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"即係港交所比d蝕錢既公司上市<br />\n係唔係咁解?"},{"pid":"9a90e66f0c2e43fd46f820